title: NFL Free Agency Teaser
itunes:title: NFL Free Agency Teaser
description:
A room filled with some heroes- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal & Chris Wesseling- discuss the latest news from around the league, including Frank Reich being named the head coach of the Colts (10:30); Minneapolis hiring John DeFilippo as their new OC (15:00); Johnny Manziel tells Good Morning America that he’s getting his life together and wants back in the NFL (22:00); Plus, the heroes take a trip into the lab as they brainstorm about some intriguing free agency options (34:00). And, check out the heroes' GoFundMe page for Wess! https://www.gofundme.com/chris-wesseling-takes-out-the-big-c
